aVI have a Ph.D in molecular biology.
p72
aVI still barely understand what most scientists are talking about.
p73
aVSo as my friend was trying to explain that experiment,
p74
aVit seemed like the more he said,
p75
aVthe less I understood.
p76
aVBecause if you're trying to give someone the big picture
p77
aVof a complex idea, to really capture its essence,
p78
aVthe fewer words you use, the better.
